data.description: Discover the modern elegance in this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home built in 2022, boasting high vaulted ceilings, a charming courtyard with a built-in BBQ grill, and a prime location near downtown Rio Grande City. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere, while the well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and an en-suite bath with a double vanity, and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms share a stylish bathroom. The courtyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, and the proximity to downtown and local amenities ensures a convenient and vibrant lifestyle. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your dream home in Rio Grande City!
